Don't use caskroom/fonts anymore
The correct way is:
brew tap homebrew/cask-fonts
brew cask install ________


---------------------------------
Fira Code Install
Copy and paste the following into your terminal: 

brew tap homebrew/cask-fonts
brew cask install \
  font-fira-code \
  font-fira-mono \
  font-fira-mono-for-powerline \
  font-fira-sans

then go to VS Code settings and for text font family just type in Fira Code and check enable ligatures
https://github.com/tonsky/FiraCode/wiki/VS-Code-Instructions
---------------------------------
